\newlabel{fig:gallery_geometric}{{12}{24}{\textbf {Geometric attacks --- all four configurations on img\_0018.} Rows: Baseline / Optimized / Multi-Ring / MR-AllChan. Numbers below each image are AUC values (50-image evaluation). Crop and rotation scramble the Fourier ring structure, making these the hardest attacks; MR-AllChan (bottom row) achieves AUC $\geq 0.980$ on all four conditions, a $\Delta $AUC $\approx 0.07$--$0.09$ gain over the single-channel baseline}{figure.caption.29}{}}
